6 priced and of comparable quality.
7 Sec. 241. Subject to sections 241a, 241b, 241c, 241e, 241f,
8 241g, 241h, 241i, 241k, 241l, and 244, the funds appropriated in
9 sections section 236 and 236d to public universities must be paid
